  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 resubmission)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. Following regulatory feedback, the model risk level has been elevated to 3 to reflect the high decision consequence and broader intended use scope. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet their required levels. The 'Use error' factor is documented as not assessed on the basis that user-induced variation is considered outside the scope of a CFD simulation study; however, this rationale conflates applicability with assessment status and the factor has not been formally scoped out or designated not-applicable.",
