    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 3. The use error factor is documented as not assessed; the assessment team's narrative argues this factor does not apply to the COU given the fixed simulation protocol, and on this basis the overall credibility package was accepted. The package is submitted with the understanding that the use error determination will be revisited if the simulation protocol is modified or executed by personnel outside the core team.",
